data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home! The high ceilings give it an airy feel, and the wood look tile floors add a touch of warmth. The open concept is perfect for modern living, and a gourmet kitchen with granite countertops and custom cabinets is a chef's delight. The primary suite sounds luxurious with its walk-in closets, garden tub, double sinks, and separate walk-in shower. Enjoy entertaining or just relaxing on the covered back patio.  Plus, being near Wylie East schools is a great bonus for families. It's a home that combines style and comfort seamlessly!
